        "description": "<p>Displays a simple widget with a list of the most commented posts.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>English and German Translation</li>\n<li>Number of Posts choosable</li>\n<li>Multiple widgets possible</li>\n<li>More Information will be added as the plugin gets better and bigger.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Features in the future</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Choose year or period of time</li>\n<li>Choose different posts types (Posts, Pages, &#8230;)</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload <code>pd-mostcommentedposts</code> to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>Drag &amp; Drop the Widget in the Widget Area</li>\n</ol>\n",
